<% provide(:title, "About") %>

<h1 class="fw-light">About StudyMates</h1>

<div class="text-muted">

  <p>
    <strong>StudyMates</strong> is a collaborative learning platform designed to help students and professionals connect,
    communicate, and grow together through shared knowledge and meaningful discussions.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h5>Our Mission</h5>
  <p>
    Our mission is to make learning more interactive and community-driven. We believe that knowledge becomes more powerful
    when it is shared, discussed, and applied collectively rather than learned in isolation.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h5>What We Offer</h5>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Collaborative Rooms:</strong> Join topic-based spaces to discuss ideas, solve problems, and learn together</li>
    <li><strong>Personalized Feed:</strong> Stay updated with rooms and discussions from people you follow and participate with</li>
    <li><strong>Community Connections:</strong> Build meaningful connections with students and professionals worldwide</li>
    <li><strong>Real-Time Messaging:</strong> Share insights, resources, and files within collaborative rooms</li>
    <li><strong>Smart Discovery:</strong> Easily find relevant topics, rooms, and users through search</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h5>Why StudyMates?</h5>
  <p>
    Traditional learning is often isolated and inefficient. StudyMates solves this by creating an environment where users
    can learn together, stay motivated, and benefit from collective intelligence.
  </p>

  <p>
    Whether you're preparing for exams, working on projects, or exploring new skills, StudyMates helps you stay connected
    with the right people at the right time.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h5>Our Values</h5>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Learning is better together</li>
    <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> Clean, intuitive, and distraction-free experience</li>
    <li><strong>Growth:</strong> Continuous learning through community interaction</li>
    <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Open to students and professionals of all backgrounds</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h5>Our Vision</h5>
  <p>
    We aim to build a global learning community where anyone can find study partners, share knowledge, and grow their skills
    in a supportive and engaging environment.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <p>
    Thank you for being part of the StudyMates community. Together, we learn better.
  </p>

</div>